title: Classical Music - Morning Mood (Grieg)
description:
Perhaps the most famous "Morning" song.  Composed by Edvard Grieg (1843-1907)
Belongs in a class by itself.  
(It is also known as "Morgenstimmung.")
No copyright intention.  None of the videos are mine.
Watch in HD (if possible).
Another great morning song is Rossini's "Morning Song" (see playlist).
